114
00:08:28,996 --> 00:08:30,396
Have you not been sleeping?

115
00:08:31,536 --> 00:08:33,335
Because of the bad loan deal?

116
00:08:35,376 --> 00:08:37,435
- Yes. - That's really it?

117
